<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>URL SHORTENER</title>
    <style>
      
      body {
        font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
         background: radial-gradient(circle,#cce3f1, #b4d8f1, #60c1f2);  
        background-size: cover; /* Ensure the image covers the entire container */
        background-position: center; /* Center the image */
        background-repeat: no-repeat; 
        height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 0;
        overflow-x: hidden; 
        overflow-y: scroll;
        border: 1px solid #ccc;
        white-space: nowrap;

       }
        .head2 {
            font-size: 10px; /* Adjust the font size for smaller screens */
        }
      
      @keyframes colorChange {
          0% { color: rgb(87, 14, 54); }
          50% { color: rgb(27, 11, 85); }
      }

      @keyframes fadeIn {
        0% { transform: translateX(0); }
        50% { transform: translateX(100px); }
        100% { transform: translateX(0); }
      }
      @keyframes bounceIn {
        0% {
          transform: scale(0.5);
          opacity: 0;
        }
        50% {
          transform: scale(1.1);
          opacity: 1;
        }
        100% {
          transform: scale(1);
        }
      }

      .head1 {
        padding-top: 20px;
        animation: bounceIn 0.9s ease-out;
        background-clip: text;        
        font-family: "Trebuchet MS", "Lucida Sans Unicode", "Lucida Grande",
          "Lucida Sans", Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 50px;
        font-style: italic;

      }
      .container {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a3d6d, #09205d);
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8),
          0 0 25px rgba(81, 186, 251, 0.8);
        width: 750px;
        text-align: center;
        animation: fadeIn 1.2s ease-in-out, glowPulse 4s infinite;
        margin-bottom: 65px;
      }

      @keyframes fadeIn {
        from {
          opacity: 0;
          transform: translateY(-50px);
        }

        to {
          opacity: 1;
          transform: translateY(0);
        }
      }

      @keyframes glowPulse {
        0%,
        100% {
          box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8),
            0 0 25px rgba(28, 70, 141, 0.8);
        }

        50% {
          box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9),
            0 0 40px rgb(56, 103, 124);
        }
      }

      .head2 {
        font-size: 32px;
        margin-bottom: 25px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff6f91, #ff9eac);
        background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        animation: slideIn 1.2s ease-in-out;
        
   
      }

      @keyframes slideIn {
        from {
          opacity: 0;
          transform: translateX(-30px);
        }

        to {
          opacity: 1;
          transform: translateX(0);
        }
      }

      label {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: #eaeaea;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        display: block;
        animation: fadeIn 1.2s ease-in-out;
      }

      #mainurl {
        padding: 10px;
        width: 90%;
        height: 100px;
        resize: none;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 10px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #50538f, #8f94fb);
        font-size: 16px;
        transition: box-shadow 0.4s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
        animation: slideIn 1.2s ease-in-out;
        color: whitesmoke;

        
      }

      #mainurl:focus {
        outline: none;
        box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(143, 148, 251, 0.8);
        transform: scale(1.05);
      }

      button {
        padding: 10px 25px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff758c, #ff9eac);
        color: #242057;
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 600;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 10px;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.4s ease;
        animation: fadeIn 1.2s ease-in-out;
      }

      button:hover {
        transform: scale(1.1);
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 182, 193, 1);
      }

      #shortt{
          color: #ffddc1;;
        }

      p {
        margin-top: -10px;
        font-size: 20px;
        color: #010c0c;
        animation: fadeIn 1.2s ease-in-out;
        align-content: center;
        line-height: 30px;
        font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
        font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif;

       
      }

      a {
        color: #fadec5;
        text-decoration: none;
        word-wrap:normal;
        font-weight: bold;
      }

      a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
        color: #ffe4e1;
      }
      .footer {
            margin-top: auto;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            padding: 10px 0;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            color: #ffffff;
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {

         
        .container {
          width: 670px;
          padding: 15px;
        }
        .head1 {
          margin-top: 100px;
          font-size: 1.5rem;
        }
        .head2 {
          font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        #mainurl {
          width: 100%;
          height: 60px;
          font-size: 12px;
        }
        button {
          padding: 6px 15px;
          font-size: 14px;
        }
        p {
          font-size: 13.6px;
          line-height: 26px;
        }
      }
      
    
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1 class="head1"><u>URL SHORTNER PROJECT</u></h1></br>
    <p>URL Shortener Project is a free tool to shorten URLs and generate short links
      <br/>URL shortener allows to create a proper shortened link making it easy to share with your network</p>
    <br>
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="head2">URL Shortener Project</h1>
      <form action="/short" method="POST">
        <label for="mainURL">Paste the URL to be shortened</label>
        <textarea
          id="mainurl"
          name="mainurl"
          rows="4"
          cols="50"
          required
        ></textarea>
      </br> </br>
        <button type="submit">Click to shorten URL</button>
      </form>
      <% if(shortURL) { %>
      <p id="shortt"><br/>
        Short URL :
        <a href="<%= shortURL %>" target="_blank"> <%= shortURL %></a>
      </p>
      <% } %>
    </div>
    <footer class="footer">
      &copy; samruddhidesai 2025. All rights reserved.
  </footer>
  </body>
</html>
